    <item>
      <title>印度法院听取了SEBI的诉讼上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/india-court-orders-corruption-probe-of-ex-market-regulator-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的一个高等法院将于周二听到针对一项特别法院命令的上诉，要求对印度证券交易委员会对印度前任负责人的经济欺诈指控进行调查，就在她的任期结束后几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/india-court-orders-corruption-probe-of-ex-market-regulator-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 05:01:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
